ethereal-0.9.8-epaplugin
========================

The following instructions explain how to compile and install the Ethereal plugin for dissecting
EPA protocol messages received on an Ethernet interface.

Unpacking
---------
Unpack and rename the ethereal 0.9.8 distribution tarball.

> tar zxvf ethereal-0.9.8.tar.gz
> mv ethereal-0.9.8 ethereal-0.9.8-epaplugin

Remove files that should be replaced by the checkout which is next.
> cd ethereal-0.9.8-epaplugin
> rm configure.in
> rm Makefile.am
> rm plugins/Makefile.am

Patch doc/Makefile.am: remove trailing backslash on last line, otherwise autogen.sh will fail
to configure the software lateron.

Checkout EPA plugin source code
-------------------------------
cd to directory above LOFAR
> cvs co LOFAR/MAC/Tools/ethereal-0.9.8-epaplugin

Configure, build and install the EPA plugin
-------------------------------------------
> cd LOFAR/MAC/Tools/ethereal-0.9.8-epaplugin
> mkdir aclocal-missing          # autogen assumes that this directory exists
> ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr
> cd plugins/epa
> make
> sudo make install  # run as root
